  "title": "*URGENT* $30/hr Locum Staff Nurse #HRY",
  "description": "<p>Working Hours;<br />34 hrs part time per week<br /><br />JobScope:</p><ul><li> Implement nursing interventions as outlined in the care plan and carry out nursing</li><li>procedures according to the care needs of the client;</li><li> Provide training and supervision to care staff;</li><li> Co-ordinate with other team members and update them on the changes in the</li><li>client's condition and needs;</li><li> Prepare clinical documentation, monitor outcomes of services, and perform</li><li>escalation of cases if there is a need for more acute management of clients;</li><li> Provide ongoing support and education to the caregiver, client, and family;</li><li> Carry out other responsibilities and duties as assigned from time to time, including</li><li>coverage of other Staff Nurse in other Senior Care facilities if necessary.</li></ul><p><br />Requirements</p><ul><li>Valid SNB and BCLS</li><li>Min 5 year exp in Geriatric / Ortho / Neuro / Gen Ward exp / acute exp / nursing home / Snr Care centre exp</li><li>Comfortable to float between 3 centres (Dover, Henderson, Queenstown) </li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please email your updated CV to rachel.lim@recruitexpress.com.sg or WA 97527630 for more information.</p><p></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p></p><p>EA Personnel No: R23116144</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Lim Ruo Yi, Rachel</p><p>Company EA license No.: Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</p>",
